; =======================================
; FINISH
; =======================================
G1 Z10 F3000           ; Raise nozzle
G1 X0 Y220 F3000       ; Move bed forward for inspection
M104 S0                ; Nozzle heater off
M140 S0                ; Bed heater off
M84                    ; Disable steppers

; =======================================
; HOW TO READ RESULTS:
;
; GOOD adhesion:
;   - Lines are flat and slightly overlap
;   - Smooth, solid surface
;   - Squares stick when you try to peel
;
; NOZZLE TOO HIGH:
;   - Lines are round, gaps between them
;   - Easy to peel off
;   - FIX: Lower Z offset by 0.05mm
;
; NOZZLE TOO LOW:
;   - Thin/transparent first layer
;   - Nozzle drags through previous lines
;   - FIX: Raise Z offset by 0.05mm
;
; UNEVEN across bed:
;   - Some squares good, some bad
;   - FIX: Re-level the bed
; =======================================
